ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. WAYNE G. DYMOND, a Judge of the Trial Division of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland and Labrador, who was required to relocate to St. John's following his reassignment on January 10, 2007.
